create table eventhubs
(
Country varchar(100),
City varchar(100),
Date varchar(100),
Temperature varchar(100),
Humidity varchar(100),
WindSpeed varchar(100),
WindDirection varchar(100),
Precipitation varchar(100),
CloudCover varchar(100),
Visibility varchar(100),
Pressure varchar(100),
DewPoint varchar(100),
UVIndex varchar(100),
Sunrise varchar(100),
Sunset varchar(100),
Moonrise varchar(100),
Moonset varchar(100),
MoonPhase varchar(100),
Conditions varchar(100),
Icon varchar(100),
EventProcessedUtcTime varchar(100),
PartitionId varchar(100),
EventEnqueuedUtcTime varchar(100)
)

select * from eventhubs
